      <title>ISS 斥責巴菲特的波克夏海瑟威氣候變遷與治理問題</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/iss-rebukes-buffetts-berkshire-hathaway-over-climate-change-governance-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四，一家領先的股東顧問公司建議波克夏海瑟威股東暫緩投票，以重新選出華倫巴菲特集團的五名董事，理由是對氣候變遷和治理的擔憂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/iss-rebukes-buffetts-berkshire-hathaway-over-climate-change-governance-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 17:15:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
